special_bonds lj 0.0 0.0 0.0 coul 0.0 0.0 0.0

group at_atoms type 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 9
group cg_atoms type 1

fix bm all backmap cg_type 1 alpha 0.0001 lambda0 0.0 nonuniform no

fix integrate at_atoms nve
fix thermo at_atoms langevin 300.0 300.0 33.3 12345

timestep 1.00

thermo 1000
thermo_style custom step temp pe ke etotal press

dump traj all custom 1000 dump.backmap id mol type x y z f_bm
dump_modify traj sort id

# Phase 1: CG equilibration
fix_modify bm active no
run 10000

# Phase 2: Backmapping
timestep 1.00
fix_modify bm active yes
run 10000

# Phase 3: AT production
timestep 1.00
run 10000
